title: General Surgeon Peter A. Innes, M.D., F.A.C.S., joins Northwest Health
description: Dr. Innes earned his medical degree from Oregon Health Sciences University in Portland, Ore. He then completed his surgical residency at University of Kansas School of Medicine at Wichita, Kan.
